column2: select     S.ra as sdss_ra, S.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec,     S.psfmag_r as r, W.w1mpro as w1 into mydb.MyTable_# from wise_xmatch as X       join wise_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr       join photoobjall as M on X.objid=M.objid     join mydb.SDSS_gal_# as S on M.objid = S.objid_#
